    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty grim outlook lol. but wouldn't someone say that the failures are just a result of how hard global diplomacy is, rather than the UN itself being broken? like, is it actually a structural failure or just how the world works right now?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
